In this JSON representation, we first state the theorem and set its status to "proved". The proof follows, first introducing the assumption that A^2 is invertible. We then define matrix B in accordance with this assumption. Next, we introduce matrix C, defined as ABA. Finally, we assert the required property of matrix C, justifying it based on the properties of matrix B and the definition of matrix C.

